## Completeness Checklist
- [ ] All NFRs have numeric, measurable targets
- [ ] All NFRs have a defined test approach in the NFR Testing Matrix
- [ ] Compliance frameworks identified and referenced per requirement
- [ ] Security classification of data and systems completed
- [ ] Performance baseline established (current state documented)
- [ ] Reviewed and approved by Solutions Architect

## Handover Readiness
<!-- Confirms this artefact is ready for inclusion in RTM and Gate B pack. -->
- [ ] All NFRs traceable to business drivers or compliance obligations
- [ ] NFR test types incorporated into draft Test Strategy
- [ ] No NFRs in conflict with each other (e.g. extreme availability vs extreme cost constraints)
- [ ] Document version controlled and stored in the project artefact repository
